snippet.title: Alchemy Story - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Alchemy story is an upcoming indie game about magic, cute creatures and adventure!

The demo is available on Itch.io!

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/confusedhamster

Itchio: https://confusedhamster.itch.io/alchemystory

Twitter: https://twitter.com/CCHamster

Music composed by Matthew Harnage! 
Website: https://www.matthewharnage.com/
